  <brief_title>Optimized Duration of Clopidogrel Therapy Following Treatment With the Endeavor - Optimize Trial</brief_title>
  <acronym>OPTIMIZE</acronym>
  <official_title>Optimized Duration of Clopidogrel Therapy Following Treatment With the Endeavor Zotarolimus - Eluting Stent in the Real World Clinical Practice - Optimize Trial</official_title>
